{"type": "article", "id": 15360, "title": "《顶层视野》", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230643ujUHMiy0sWYeFp1K.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/mn/detailApp/ref=asc_df_B00XM8OWBA1759353/?asin=B00XM8OWBA&amp;tag=douban-23&amp;creative=2384&amp;creativeASIN=B00XM8OWBA&amp;linkCode=df0\" target=\"_blank\">《顶层视野：塑造我们世界的领导力》</a>，D. 迈克尔·林赛(D. Michael Lindsay)<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>对这本书印象深刻是因为它写了白宫学者那套机制，我觉得挺牛的。很多企业需要的人都是挖不来的，比如美团的城市经理，怎么挖？只能自己培养、批量造。我觉得这个机制是有启发意义的，虽然这样说起来好功利。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}